2004-10-03  Jp Calderone  <exarkun@twistedmatrix.com>

	* twisted/mail/imap4.py, twisted/mail/test/test_imap.py:
	Changed the values for the attributes of Header objects
	created when parsing BODY[HEADER] requests.  negate will
	now be True instead of False and fields will not be ()
	instead of None.  This causes the Header instance to appear
	identical to that created by parsing BODY[HEADER.FIELDS.NOT ()].

2004-10-03  Jp Calderone  <exarkun@twistedmatrix.com>

	* twisted/mail/pop3.py, twisted/mail/test/test_pop3client.py:
	Added Quotient's nicer POP3 client and tests.  Deprecated the
	old POP3Client.

